verbose_text: The bile acid tauroursodeoxycholic acid (TUDCA), an inhibitor of cell stress, inhibited Th17 cell differentiation and counteracted the effect of hypoglycemia, osmotic stress, and hypoxia (XREF_FIG A, 4B, and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G).
